reviews.title: Lovely but..
reviews.comment: Awesome wallpaper! My friends love it and so do i. The only thing is.. I\'ve noticed that is drains my battery really quickly and usually last me the whole day.. Is there any way possible for it to have a minimal effect of battery life?

reviews.title: Good wallpaper
reviews.comment: This is a pretty solid nyan cat live wallpaper. It has very minimal effect on battery life. My main complaint is that it\'s not very customizable, and you have to unlock some options by playing the game for a long time. But as a wallpaper it does what you would expect. I just wish I could make the cat larger.
